description:
Welcome to the placeholder September SWmobile tech talk event.

This will be our first tech talk meetup in a while and looking forward to hosting some great talks! If you are keen to speak please fill in the CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

Looking forward to seeing you there!

* TBC

If you are keen to speak at a future event please fill in the CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

See you there!
title: September Tech Talk Night
